    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a car that doesn't just drive, but breathes life into the open road. This exquisite masterpiece is a rare survivor, boasting a finish so deep and lustrous it mirrors the sky itself. Every curve tells a story of meticulous care, and the interior welcomes you with the scent of premium heritage and the promise of endless horizons. To sit behind the wheel is to step into a curated dream, where the mechanical harmony is so perfect, the world outside simply fades away. This is more than a vehicle; it is a legacy waiting for its next curator.",
      "price": 48500.0,
