      "description": "Offered is a superlative specimen of engineering, maintained to a standard that surpasses original factory tolerances. This chassis exhibits zero lash throughout the drivetrain, with a suspension geometry that remains crisp and communicative. The powerplant has been kept on a strict synthetic-only diet, ensuring optimal thermal management and peak volumetric efficiency across the entire rev range. Every bushing and seal has been scrutinized for structural integrity, resulting in a tactile driving experience that mirrors its showroom-floor debut. This is a concours-level opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and uncompromising performance metrics.",
